分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=c7515e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"2218384cff3a69f6a5876e563dc88ec057a49ff4","tid":2032670,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca0ba4ebe51c5868356f988a94f5c9ef63e1ce8f","tid":2032670,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e7b7d285be6dc161182693b825803dcd1b54aa97","tid":2032670,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:49:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1731d53fbc4c87febefa50617fbc0e9a09e0443","tid":2032670,"uid":70183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"就算今日燒撚左政總都唔會有改變<br />\n<br />\n唔係我地失敗<br />\n<br />\n我地要贏就要長命過佢"},{"pid":"76de05649d7d4e995bb357b274acec183438418f","tid":2032670,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b9